Text: Chinese food secret. They normally should have some kind of stir fry veg like broccoli in garlic sauce with rice. Or a tofu dish. Thatâ€™s normally my go to. Spring rolls are about 100-150 cals as well.

Author: sidetoad
Text: A title fit to strike fear in the hearts of any ED sufferer  Sorry to hear this, I absolutely hate when surprise meals come up! Just remember it's only one night, weight is determined by the stacking of choices over time, no single one can destroy or set us up anywhere, even if that's what our EDs always want to make us believe. Hope you were still able to enjoy your time with the people you went with at least!
